translated: Brunskog, Herbert, Architect SAR, Linköping, b. 16/9/14 in Örebro to civil engineer V.H.B. and Jenny Koraen. Married in 1940 to Gunilla Brunskog. Children: Lars b. 1942, Elsa b. 1945. Completed Latin and Real science high school in 1933 and 1934 respectively in Eskilstuna. Received an architect degree from KTH in 1938. Studied abroad in Denmark in 1937, and in Germany, Czechoslovakia, Switzerland and Italy in 1938. Worked at Axel V. Brunskog's architect office and also had his own architect business.
